    "causal_summary": "Phase 001 of the numbered-prefix deprecation. Update the two authoritative sk-doc convention skills (create-feature-catalog, create-manual-testing-playbook), their asset templates, and the /create:* command generators so the documented canonical category-folder name is the bare descriptive slug, not NN--slug. Ordering is documented as owned by the root index table. Docs-only phase — no folders are renamed here; it removes the mandate that would otherwise re-introduce numbers.",
